Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是南極嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.57,0:00:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到南極啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.07,0:00:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡就是南極啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}女高中生們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.62,0:00:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很好 100公斤內沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吃了那麼多點心 重量居然沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.17,0:00:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你再想想點心去哪了 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的要搭那個去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不能搭雪地車去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.35,0:00:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}結月 怎麼一副要死了的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.60,0:00:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真有要死的心情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:00:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的是好大的船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你先看看再說啊
