Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原地趴下來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}並不冷？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡12月是夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}碰上溫暖的日子 有時白天溫度不會降到冰點以下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的不冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在行李送到 忙起來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我帶你們快速參觀一下基地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡就是昭和基地…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個像是立方體堆成的建築是管理樓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用家打比方的話 就是所有人會聚一起的客廳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是發電樓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:03:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這些是居住樓和倉庫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是湖濱旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}湖濱？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們幫夏季隊的宿舍取的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過冬的隊員 一般會住在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過三年沒來了 那邊短時間也整頓不完
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再考慮到你們是女生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以你們各自有單人房
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡的家具都可以用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡的空氣很乾燥 準備好迎接靜電吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過地板有供暖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且拉開百葉窗的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終於不用擔心小理成天說夢話了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我那麼會說夢話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}超會的 你總是眼睛一睜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}壺魔人不肯出廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯定通不過檢票了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼壺魔人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下來本來要去管理樓的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但行李也快要送過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們回直升機停機坪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個肯定得換一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來打掃一番囉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下一波送到前休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還撐得住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒問題 我有在搬家公司打過工
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那休息10分鐘 就幫我去那邊裝貨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我收到封簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛剛我們在基地裡的時候 可能就發到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}管理樓附近能收到電波訊號的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在南極也能用手機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是企鵝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別叫那麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小結 準備拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}保持五公尺外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:08.51,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}企…鵝！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我開拍了 小結準備開始報導
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:13.43,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}往我們這邊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來了 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}停停停停 笨蛋 保持五公尺距離
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}站住站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真會鬧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以把髒雪倒進去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說是等會要過濾的 可以倒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你脫掉會曬傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都喘不上氣了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說 要做的事真是一個接一個的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三年沒人來過這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這陣子大概都得這麼忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不想做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有忙碌才是最能推動錶針前進的事！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又是你隨口說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是我在便利商店打工時想的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我大概是喜歡忙忙碌碌的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好累
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也不討厭忙忙碌碌的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這段旅途是我們一起走過來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一起聊了很多 也玩了很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你突然問些什麼東西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}電視劇？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}出發前我參加了試鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}招的是晨間劇裡 主角的摯友角色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會吧 你被選中了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:06.34,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康中特圓體\bord0\fs20\1c&HD9D7CF&\frz10.05\frx334\fry0\pos(316,80)}發給：白石結月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:06.34,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康中特圓體\bord0\b0\fs25\1c&H6D7179&\frz10.05\frx324\fry2\pos(508,92)}漂亮！中了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:06.34,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康中特圓體\bord0\b0\fs25\1c&H6D7179&\frx336\fry0\frz9.463\pos(710,146)}晨間劇試鏡通過了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:06.34,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康中特圓體\bord0\b0\fs25\1c&H6D7179&\frx336\fry0\frz9.463\pos(730,192)}恭喜你！你真棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:06.34,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康中特圓體\bord0\b0\fs25\1c&H6D7179&\frx336\fry0\frz9.463\pos(622,280)}記得照顧好自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:06.34,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康中特圓體\bord0\b0\fs25\1c&H6D7179&\frx336\fry0\frz9.463\pos(634,324)}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:06.34,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康中特圓體\bord0\b0\fs25\1c&H6D7179&\frx336\fry0\frz9.463\pos(648,370)}本訊息來自myPhone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好歸好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是要拍電視劇就會沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不能像這樣和你們在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不想要這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但就算沒有電視劇 我們也是各過各的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒關係 大家都是摯友了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}摯友…我們是摯友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別哭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但你之前說過啊 大家都才認識的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們那時確實才認識不久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼時候變成摯友了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我還在北海道的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被我說中了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:08:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就你們三個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瞞著我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總之 我們從沒有瞞著你做過什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你疑心病真重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像只有一件事沒告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是我們四個確實是朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從什麼時候開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼時候…不知不覺中？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所謂朋友就是這麼回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是從沒有人跟我說想當朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天也好好加油吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼時候開始變成朋友啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她肯定一直等人跟她說想當朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我們來跟她說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣簡直像我逼你們說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別演了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理怎麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰知道呢 她說包在她身上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但她膽小和膽大的一面都挺極端的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安全帽戴了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安全帽戴了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:31.90,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康中特圓體\bord10\fs45\b0\3c&H47C0D5&\pos(512,140)}午餐菜單{\i1}！{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:31.90,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康中特圓體\bord6\fs45\b0\1c&H7E62B6&\3c&HE4E3D8&\pos(512,140)}午餐菜單{\i1}！{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:31.90,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnMMarkerHK-Bold\bord0\fs65\1c&H907761&\pos(396,290)}聖誕節南極特別菜單
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}繩子綁緊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}繩子綁緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}臉色正常嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}臉色正常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}靴子穿好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}靴子穿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天一天也好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}注意安全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}注意安全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說好的室內工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡比室外還冷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鼻子都凍紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都說要省電了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}室內工作動作要快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這些就是全部了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下來麻煩你們處理這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雞？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:10:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為是聖誕節啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們找個暖和的地方 幫它解凍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然我昨天開始就準備了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但感覺還不太夠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}暖和的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就拜託你們啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後你們兩個就留在這裡幫我的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那邊肯定最好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管怎麼看都太危險了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就給太陽曬曬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想 反正是永晝 太陽不會落下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這也是鳥肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他們該吃還是會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且還有企鵝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}連雞肉都不放過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我哪知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:41.34,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn@華康中特圓體\b0\bord0\1c&H555C5D&\frz275.6\pos(484,238)}敢碰就讓你下地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說你那邊沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 完美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天的點心完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是豪華
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難得的聖誕節嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有這麼重要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們知道基地生活中什麼最重要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吃飯和節日活動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}畢竟每天都在有限的區域內過單調的生活嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}點心時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聖誕節蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聖誕快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聖誕快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不喜歡聖誕節嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}倒也說不上討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要說的話就跟慶祝生日一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很不公平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明每個人都有生日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有人能得到他人的祝賀 有人卻不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的歌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}外面要先拍嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對啊 說是風勢變強就可能會禁止外出了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}關於之前的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我決定要參演電視劇了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 我考慮了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯定有不少人期待我出演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我想拜託各位一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個 能請你們簽字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:34.46,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\p1\fscx1800\fscy2400\bord1\1c&HE5E7E7&\1a&H50&\pos(1082,260)}m -10 10 l -10 -10 l 10 -10 l 10 10
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:34.46,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\fn華康芸風體W3\bord0\fs60\1c&H5D4D48&\fsp-15\pos(958,20)}友情起誓書
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:34.46,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\fn華康采風體W3\bord0\fs25\1c&H6C6160&\pos(906,88)}①請和我白石結月約定成為朋友\N\N\N②請和我約定，就算這趟旅行結\N\h\h\h\h束了，我們的友情也絕對不會\N\h\h\h\h改變\N\N\N③請和我約定，不管相隔多遠，\N\h\h\h\h我們的友情都會持續下去\N\N\N④請和我約定，不管多久沒見，\N\h\h\h\h我們的友情都會持續下去\N\N\N⑤請和我約定，以後只要有時間\N\h\h\h\h，務必抽空聚一聚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:34.46,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\fn華康楷書體W5\bord0\fs20\1c&H605B5D&\pos(902,452)}請在下方簽名，證明你做過上述五條約定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即使這趟旅行結束 很多時候不在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也能心安了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.46,0:13:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這種東西沒有意義
