Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒有信心跟她說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道放著不管嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可沒這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小結
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別擔心 她可沒有生你的氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是小理都哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她只是有點寂寞吧
