Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別踢皮球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我做了什麼怪事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其實…也不是什麼怪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我站在你的立場上 我也會那麼想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聖誕快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我覺得朋友不是嘴上說說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我經常聽人這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那朋友究竟是什麼？
