Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以說是種…感覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比方說小結喜歡小理
