Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:56.28,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}聽見一聲輕輕的「想見你」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:19:04.58,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}聲音漸漸消失在了空中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:22.34,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我的心底依然在暗自動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:29.94,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}雪白閃耀的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:38.49,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我們踩下的足跡 漸漸褪去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:46.45,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}原以為這些時光 永無止境
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:54.71,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}卻突然畫上了句號
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:20:04.51,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}所以這份心情 我不會忘懷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:13.98,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}它比任何語言 都要寶貴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:23.24,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}總有一天 會再度牽起你我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:35.29,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}帶著我們 又一次踏上旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:46.14,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}所以這些時光 我不會忘懷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:55.77,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}你我一道 度過的珍貴點滴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:21:04.91,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}想必它們 會永遠牽起你我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:15.04,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}直到永遠 直到永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:20.34,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「現在在上課啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「在睡覺啦」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「在考慮要不要回覆吧」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我能猜到她是什麼表情 很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對我而言 朋友大概就是這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然我也不怎麼清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但大概就是這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起 可能幫不上你什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聖誕快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}AND
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生日快樂！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}結月 你生日之前剛過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但那時我們一直在暈船 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以小理提議在南極幫你過生日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還請弓子小姐分了我們一些材料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒做好的部分 就麻煩你用想像彌補啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}結月 生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快吹蠟燭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛見面時也是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人家才沒哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不趕快吹就要融化了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}結月～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為…這是第一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有朋友幫我慶生…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快吹吧 結月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人家的第一次啊…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}點心時間到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
